      • performEndOfDayProcedure

        void performEndOfDayProcedure(IConnectionPoint connectionPoint,
                              String parameter)
        Perform end of day procedure. The end of day procedure can be triggered from the command line, scheduled using the Scheduler or invoked programmatically by calling this method.
        Parameters:
        connectionPoint - The connection point upon which to perform the procedure (only used by multi-connection point components).
        parameter - A component-specific string to be interpreted by the executor.
